He resigned here, but I don't think he should have. The point is 18...eitherNxd7 19. Nxe7+. If 18...Rxd7 19. Rxd7 eitherNxd7 20. Nxe7+. However, their are other moves and he doesn't have to take it. If any one feels he should resign this position let me know. I think that the point of this annotation is to tell people not to stop at one or two moves. Really analyze if you feel you are lost.
